<!-- Header -->
![header](https://capsule-render.vercel.app/api?type=<%= header.type %>&height=<%= header.height %>&color=<%= header.color %>&text=<%= encodeURIComponent(header.text) %>&section=header&reversal=false&desc=<%= encodeURIComponent(header.desc) %>&fontAlignY=<%= header.fontAlignY %>&descAlignY=<%= header.descAlignY %>&descSize=<%= header.descSize %>)

<div align="center">
<%_ if (cards.hasStats) { _%>
    <img src="./assets/stats.svg" alt="<%= username %>'s GitHub stats" style="height: 220px;">
<%_ } _%>
<%_ if (cards.hasLangs) { _%>
    <img src="./assets/top-langs.svg" alt="Top Langs" style="height: 220px;">
<%_ } _%>
</div>

<!-- Body -->
<% for (const [groupName, items] of Object.entries(badges)) { %>

### **<%= groupName %>**
<% for (const b of items) { %>![<%= b.label %>](https://img.shields.io/badge/<%= b.label %>-<%= b.color %>.svg?&style=for-the-badge&logo=<%= b.logo %>&logoColor=white)
<% } %>
<% } %>

![story](https://capsule-render.vercel.app/api?type=<%= storyBanner.type %>&height=<%= storyBanner.height %>&color=<%= storyBanner.color %>&text=<%= encodeURIComponent(storyBanner.text) %>&section=header&reversal=false&fontAlignY=55&descAlignY=80&descSize=25&fontColor=<%= storyBanner.fontColor %>&stroke=ffffff&strokeWidth=2)

## 경력 및 프로젝트

### 📖 History
<% for (const item of career.history) { %>
- <%= item %>
<% } %>

### **Working**
- <%= career.working %>

### 🚀 Projects
<% for (const proj of career.projects) { %>

**<%= proj.period %>** | **<%= proj.title %>**
<% for (const d of proj.details) { %>
- <%= d %>
<% } %>
<% } %>
<% if (pinnedRepos.length > 0) { %>

### 📌 Pinned Repositories
<% for (const repo of pinnedRepos) { %>
- [**<%= repo.name %>**](<%= repo.url %>) — <%= repo.description %> ⭐ <%= repo.stars %>
<% } %>
<% } %>

![blog](https://capsule-render.vercel.app/api?type=<%= blogBanner.type %>&height=<%= blogBanner.height %>&color=<%= blogBanner.color %>&text=<%= encodeURIComponent(blogBanner.text) %>&fontSize=<%= blogBanner.fontSize %>&reversal=false)

<div align="center">
<% for (const post of blogPosts) { %>

#### [📝 <%= post.title %>](<%= post.link %>)</br>
<% } %>
</div>
